{"tid":835964,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[又係IKON] iKON具晙會曬北野武簽名被粉絲勸阻 導演曾發表過厭韓言論","createTime":"2018-09-25T10:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T13:51:31.000Z","uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3064f14b4805ce1c1f64f5b5a9ba3466e5fa6db7","tid":835964,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180925/36e88ecec68e4f1c8dc55ffb2d6e6402.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180925%2F36e88ecec68e4f1c8dc55ffb2d6e6402.jpeg&h=548934ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20180925/f2dc0674cf9c4be39e63ff57b0784fa3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com%2Fimages%2F20180925%2Ff2dc0674cf9c4be39e63ff57b0784fa3.jpeg&h=487e4888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\niKON成員具晙會在個人SNS上上傳了日本導演兼喜劇演員北野武的簽名並寫道：&ldquo;感謝北野武先生。請參加iKON的演唱會。&rdquo;因北野武過去曾有發表過厭韓爭議的言論，所以粉絲在具晙會的SNS下進行了留言忠告。該粉絲留言中表示：&ldquo;北野武有厭韓嫌疑，請刪除跟他有關的內容。&rdquo;隨後，具晙會回复粉絲：&ldquo;請不要對我指手畫腳，我不喜歡。&rdquo;表達了自己的立場。<br />\n<br />\n對於具晙會展示與厭韓演藝人關係親密的行為是個人喜好，還是認可厭韓的言論？粉絲之間的爭論也越來越激烈。&ldquo;請回應一下粉絲的請求吧&rdquo;&ldquo;這次是作為韓國代表愛豆的失誤了&rdquo;此後，具晙會刪除了相關的文字和圖片。<br />\n<br />\n北野武曾在韓劇《冬日戀歌》在日本風靡一時之際發表過，&ldquo;應該看強佔獨島（竹島）國家的電視劇嗎?&rdquo;以及&ldquo;韓國人漂亮的原因是整容手術&rdquo;等具有爭議的言論。<br />\n<br />\n另外，iKON正在以10月1日回歸的新專輯《NEW KIDS:THE FINAL》準備和亞洲巡演一起進行中。26日，iKON即將在日本發售專輯《RETURN》。<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\nBig Bang師弟來台開唱 竟大喊「中國的粉絲！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/832447/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/832447/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係時候入下雪櫃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4790cfb5bd82b4aab3d310c887e4c2c66196d84c","tid":835964,"uid":132587,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:17:19.000Z","msg":"隊野摺柒左佢啦好嘛<br />\n成班自戀獸以為自己好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf876d66cdbbc4c62343628d87ccf9e852d14ba8","tid":835964,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4790cfb5bd82b4aab3d310c887e4c2c66196d84c","tid":835964,"uid":132587,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:17:19.000Z","msg":"隊野摺柒左佢啦好嘛<br />\n成班自戀獸以為自己好紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T10:35:27.000Z","msg":"只係識有個叫波比<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好紅?"},{"pid":"f41396aa4d7f96f0f1c9160f3ad9cfdc0aaf28ba","tid":835964,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:03:50.000Z","msg":"新北市d fd"},{"pid":"13860d0cca80b600d59b32cf440b48c62a3f601b","tid":835964,"uid":207580,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"Ikon班垃圾就收檔啦<br />\n淨係bi打隊友同笑外國籍idol口音已經夠仆街"},{"pid":"fd6e0173f1e2f614e0371e89a24864a1a120a461","tid":835964,"uid":193951,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"究竟全盛時期既IKON可以做幾多on9嘢?"},{"pid":"2d2a5e354b3f15b8e33e669958ab0d5048871a0f","tid":835964,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13860d0cca80b600d59b32cf440b48c62a3f601b","tid":835964,"uid":207580,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:05:44.000Z","msg":"Ikon班垃圾就收檔啦<br />\n淨係bi打隊友同笑外國籍idol口音已經夠仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:25:20.000Z","msg":"咩事"},{"pid":"38b85808e0930a0884ff4f7eae88f79486953252","tid":835964,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd6e0173f1e2f614e0371e89a24864a1a120a461","tid":835964,"uid":193951,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T12:08:1